            <p class="desc_comp_tav">&emsp;&emsp; <b>Q: What is Commoviecator?</br></br></b>"Commoviecator is a competition by Television and Film Student Union under Epicentrum event by the Faculty of Communication Science Universitas Padjadjaran. Commoviecator is held with the purpose to be the student’s forum to emerge their communication skills through short movie. The main concept of Commoviecator is that a movie is not just a work of art, but also a tool to communicate."</p>
            <p class="desc_comp_tav">&emsp;&emsp; <b>Q: How to register as a participant for the Commoviecator competition? (Registration Timeline)</br></b>
