				<li>Participants must pay registration fee : Rp80.000,00</li>
				<li>The film has the theme of “Social Climate : Through Human Lens”.</li>
				<li>The films that are made do not provoke people to commit racism or pornographic acts.</li>
				<li>Copyright infringement and lawsuits against works entered in the competition are not the responsibility of the organizing committee.</li>
				<li>Maximum duration of the film is 15 minutes (not including credit title).</li>
				<li>The film is your own work, not someone else’s work.</li>
				<li>Films must be given English subtitles, without exception.</li>
